data.description: To find a house with acreage is like looking for a needle in a haystack so check out this new listing!!! Welcome to this home that sits on a rolling 3.43+/- acres with large trees in Westside School District! It has 3 bedrooms and 3 bathrooms with a full basement and a few extra rooms that could be used for an office, playroom, etc.! The main floor and basement each have its own kitchen and living area as well as laundry area. A new roof was put on this home last year and it has just been completely repainted. It has a detached 2 car garage with a fenced in back yard. Another great feature is the wood burning backup heat source. This house won't last long so call an agent to schedule a private showing! More inside pictures coming this week!
